description:
Gameplay version. All mechs available from 3014.

Adds 31 Inner Sphere OmniMech variants to the game.

Blackjack II - 7 variants
Firestarter - 9 variants
Owens - 6 variants
Strider - 5 variants
Templar - 4 variants

Required mods:
Yet Another Mech Lab
Yet Another Weapon Mod
